data.description: Updated and BACK ON THE MARKET! This attractively priced home is ready for its new owners!  The sellers have secured their dream home, and now it's your turn at 408 Monticello Drive!     This 4-bed, 2-bath haven, spanning 2,036 sqft, comes with all the essential updates, including a brand new roof installed in November, upgraded plumbing, inspected AC, and more. Inside, you'll find two family rooms, 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, a shotgun-style kitchen and dining area, a laundry room, and a two-car garage.  Step outside to your private backyard retreat featuring a spacious 30,000-gallon pool, a delightful chicken coop, a serene pergola, and a fire pit – perfect for hosting gatherings during the upcoming holidays.    Seize this unique opportunity to own a piece of tranquility in the sought-after Glen Arden Heights community, close to convenient amenities, shopping, and excellent schools!    RENOVATION FINANCING AVAILABLE: all program types!  Renovation tip*- Add a third bathroom and customize the additional two to best fit you!
